headline: Charter Earnings Miss Estimates in Q4, Revenues Decline Y/Y
summary: CHTR misses Q4 earnings expectations as revenues decline, with weakness in video and political ads partly offset by mobile and Internet growth.

headline: CMCSA Q4 Earnings Beat On Theme Parks and Peacock Strength
summary: Comcast tops Q4 EPS and revenues as Theme Parks and Peacock surge, offset by broadband losses, weaker Studios results and margin pressure.
